The Future of Reading is NowBring your content to the dominant digital medium: Mobile


























 
Why Mobile?
Billions of people across the globe rely on their smartphones for consumption of information, entertainment and connecting with the world around them.Today there are over 4 billion mobile users globally.In just 3 years (2020), it is projected that this number will surpass 6.2 billion. There has never been a personal device as powerful as the smartphone. The reading experience becomes dynamic and engaging when content leverages a smartphone's capabilities.​​Let us show you how.
 


















Join the Movement
The mobile audience is now 2x that of the average desktop audience.Nearly one in eight internet users are now mobile only.The average person spends just under 3 hours per day on mobile.​​© comScore, Inc. Proprietary.​
 






 
























 
A True Mobile Experience
Frustrated with trying to read PDF on your smartphone?Tired of endless scrolling?You are not alone. Creating true mobile content is not simple.It requires a new lens.A new way of thinking about and delivering content.Cut and paste won't work.PDF doesn't work.You have to think about the size.Smaller screen, yet vastly larger potential for interactivity and engagement. A new world awaits. Manuals, Training Guides, Journals, and Books will never look the same.Welcome to the Future of Reading.  
 













Is your content ready? 




