Gadget Software partners with design firm, Second Melody



		12/21/2016
	




 

Gadget Software announced today that it will be adding new style guides, content themes and design language to its industry leading Gadget ONE mobile publishing platform. Gadget Software is partnering with Second Melody to further enhance the Gadget ONE platform. Second Melody, a digital design studio is located in Morristown, New Jersey and specializes in digital design and user experience.       








 


CEO and Chief Product Officer to Speak at Innovation Seminar for the STM Association



		12/5/2016
	




 

 CEO, Dan Crain and Chief Product Officer, Max Riggsbee are heading to London, England to speak at the STM Innovation Seminar for STM Week on Wednesday, December 7th.  The conference covers many topics including what is hot on the web right now. They will be speaking in a flash session consisting of new startups in the STM industry.​You can check out the full schedule for the event here:http://www.stm-assoc.org/events/innovations-seminar-2016/About the AssociationSTM is the leading global trade association for academic and professional publishers. It has over 120 members in 21 countries who each year collectively publish nearly 66% of all journal articles and tens of thousands of monographs and reference works. STM members include learned societies, university presses, private companies, new starts and established players.http://www.stm-assoc.org/about-stm/about-the-association/ 








 


