        App Screenshots
      





















        App Store Description
      

SchoolBuilder Mobilize is a new product in a suite that puts students at the center of the educational journey, and surrounds them with communication, engagement and enlightenment for success in their native mobile driven world. SchoolBuilder Mobilize – powered by Gadget Software – is the first mobile end-to-end product developed to give students a seamless and connected educational journey, fully supportive of the classroom and after-school experience. Our multi-purpose platform enables administrators to drive their mobile strategies for schools and organizations who want to proactively communicate and engage students in our mobile-driven world. SchoolBuilder Mobilize for K-12 schools offers administrators to communicate effectively to the entire school community and consolidate items like general information, sports/clubs, field trips, safety, and guidance center activities, and closely transitions students to admissions processes in colleges and universities.SchoolBuilder Mobilize for Higher Education gives community colleges, four-year schools, universities and graduate schools the ability to recruit students from networked schools, and extend the student experience over the device that is most native to them, while offering a connected experience for their campus life, studying abroad and collegiate sports and organizations.What’s your student-centric mobile strategy?Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.







